---
description: >
  Remove the `<span>` with `.sr-only` class from within the progress bar to
  show a visible percentage. To ensure that the label text remains legible even
  for low percentages, consider adding a `min-width` to the progress bar.
bootstrap: http://getbootstrap.com/components/#progress-label
---
<div class="progress">
  <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="60" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 60%;">
    60%
  </div>
</div>
